<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.2">
<l>tantai taḷaikaḻalat tōṉṟippō yāyppāṭi</l>
<l>nantaṉ kulamatalai yāyvaḷarntāṉ kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>nantaṉ kulamatalai yāyvaḷarntāṉ nāṉmukaṟkut</l>
<l>tantaikā ṇentai perumāṉkāṇ cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! Going and appearing to loosen the fetters of his father,</l>
<l>He grew up in the herder village as a child in Nanda’s clan.</l>
<l>See [this]! The one who grew up as a child in Nanda’s clan was the father</l>
<l>Of four-faced [Brahmā]. See my lord father! Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
